From: Marcin FM <marcin@lgic.pl>
Subject: [PATCH] Drop the unavailable simdutf embedder-test dependency

The reduced Fedora package builds the shared PDFium library and performs a
direct FPDF C API smoke test. It does not build PDFium's embedder-test targets.
Avoid requiring the separately pinned Chromium simdutf source merely while GN
parses this unused test-only target.

--- a/testing/BUILD.gn
+++ b/testing/BUILD.gn
@@ -202,6 +202,5 @@ source_set("embedder_test_support") {
     "//testing/gmock",
     "//testing/gtest",
-    "//third_party/simdutf",
   ]
   public_deps = [
     ":test_environments",
